      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im a wellness coach for a big tech firm. i need some tips i can give my clients on how to look more \"professional\" and \"authoritative\" when they're heading into big boardroom meetings with executives. like, what are the unspoken rules for grooming and appearance so they actually get taken seriously?",
